OL,3,CRobert Peston: PM's future is all down
OL,4,Cto Streeting
OL,6,FIt's now all about Wes Streeting, the
OL,7,Fhealth secretary, who has made clear
OL,8,Fhe both wants to be the UK's next
OL,9,Fprime minister, but also does not want
OL,10,Fto be the first mover in an attempted
OL,11,Fcoup against the prime minister.
OL,13,FHis difficulty is that many of those
OL,14,FMPs calling for the PM to go are his
OL,15,Fsupporters. His team insist that they
OL,16,Fare doing so without his instructions,
OL,17,Fbut few in parliament regard that as
OL,18,Feither credible or relevant.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
