OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778591472
OL,3,CRobert Peston: PM's future is all down
OL,4,Cto Streeting
OL,6,FOne of those who would support him
OL,7,Ftold me: "Too many of his people have
OL,8,Fbeen marched up a hill, that he will
OL,9,Fhave to launch a bid if Keir doesn't
OL,10,Fgo."
OL,12,FThe prime minister told the cabinet
OL,13,Fjust now that he will not set out a
OL,14,Ftimetable for his departure. He said:
OL,15,F"The Labour Party has a process for
OL,16,Fchallenging a leader and that has not
OL,17,Fbeen triggered."
OL,19,FHe might have added, "I'm looking at
OL,20,Fyou, Wes."
OL,26,@oD@JOUrD@DO]wD@AOUyD@PO]{D@VOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
