CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1778591472
OL,3,CRobert Peston: PM's future is all down
OL,4,Cto Streeting
OL,6,FFor Streeting, this is a bit of a
OL,7,Fnightmare.
OL,9,FIf he does challenge Starmer, he may
OL,10,Flose and wreck his political career.
OL,11,FAnd if he doesn't challenge Starmer in
OL,12,Fa formal contest, he may alienate his
OL,13,Fsupporters, who have stuck their heads
OL,14,Fabove the parapet at great potential
OL,15,Fcost to their political futures, and
OL,16,Fthat may fatally damage his leadership
OL,17,Fprospects forever.
OL,19,FIt's Streeting's moment in history.
OL,20,FHow will he shape it?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
